Hi. 
================

I am Saahil. 
--------------

Graduate student of Computer Science at Technical University of Munich. Focussing on Machine Learning and Empirical Software Engineering. I love summer, Led Zeppelin, coffee, fruit cakes and books. I dislike winters, shaving, mushrooms, first-person shooters and exams very much. 

I am on [twitter](http://twitter.com/saahil), [facebook](http://facebook.com/saahil.ognawala),  and [LinkedIn](http://www.linkedin.com/in/saahilognawala)
